snippet.title: The Fibos - Cosmic Invasion Gameplay
snippet.description:
This is the first full gameplay without cutscens, it captured from a finished demo and a download link will be available soon in our website and  social pages as well on our indiegogo campaign.

If you liked our game and want to support us help us to spread the word or back us on Indiegogo.
